{
  "stem": "25591.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They knew that these were Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know if they knew about Wallenberg or not, but they knew that these were Jews who were hiding there, living there, waiting for the Soviet troops to come in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made it very clear that they will not harm us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, in fact, did not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Subsequently, and they gave us-- I remember one of the things we got was a large sack of potatoes from them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One of the things that-- that became a very interesting aspect of my life as 1945 winter gave way to spring, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] everybody was poor.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the criminal elements could not take your jewelery or-- or valuables because you had no jewelry, and you had no valuables.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they took your clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people sort of walked in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were no street cars or any other transportation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that the newspapers were full of these hilarious cartoons of the husband going home to his wife naked.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she's outraged, and he explained that he just ran into somebody who took his clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had-- they-- they never took my clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I remember on two occasions, some very large, muscular, hefty Russian military women expressed some interest in me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I ran like a jackrabbit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I ran faster than they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I retained my-- my-- my dignity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But these are very lively times and very turbulent times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and after a few months, school reopened, and I went back and finished my high school education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then I was-- then I applied, ironically, first to the Medical University of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was accepted, and I attended medical school very briefly.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
